rComments: Tbh second worst professor I've had in my 4 years; she is a nice professor but grading wise, she is unreasonably hard. Does not take present any information but expect students to carry on discussions; would not take again because of her marking!

She is very nice and a available for students but the layout of the course was ridiculous. It was all seminar and discussion, which she will call on you. If you fall behind a little your pretty much screwed and there is just overall way too much going on and assignments were unclear. The course was very inaccessible as well

This prof runs the course like a seminar expecting everyone to participate in answering discussion questions while we are on an online format (zoom) with 20+ students. This class is not a seminar. Unless you enjoy hearing everyone repeat the same points to receive participation don't take this course.

Really nice person but not a good teacher. The criteria for assignments was unclear. Very tough marker and deducts points for grammar. Participation was worth 20% of our mark (during covid-19). Wouldn't recommend.
